I grew up in Austin, TX, and eventually met the most wonderful woman in the world, Katie, and married her in 2005.  I’ve been shooting photos for about the past 4 years now and I love it.  My photos have been shown in the Hope Arts Festival, and soon to appear in a book about art.  I’m currently a student at Texas State University finishing a BFA in Communication Design, and working for Precision Camera.  We’re here in Austin for a while, but may eventually move to Istanbul...
 
about me
If you’re interested in any of the photos for purchase, trade, or whatever, or you just want to make a comment, you can email me at
shaun@shaunfoxphotography.com
 
I’m also available on a contract basis for commissioned work.
